00:29:43,280 --> 00:29:46,580
so she really shouldn't be taking medicine randomly.

502
00:29:47,060 --> 00:29:51,530
I mean, seriously. What would she do without me?

503
00:29:51,530 --> 00:29:54,889
You did an amazing job this time, Huan Er.

504
00:29:54,889 --> 00:29:58,410
I, Qian Li Na, raised a great daughter!

505
00:29:58,410 --> 00:30:02,260
I totally understand the sense of fulfillment you get from helping others.

506
00:30:02,260 --> 00:30:07,010
But listen, pharmacy isn't as simple as you think.

507
00:30:09,160 --> 00:30:11,120
We'll see about that.

508
00:30:11,120 --> 00:30:13,440
All right. You really are my child.

509
00:30:13,440 --> 00:30:16,120
You acted just like me when I was young. Wait right here.

510
00:30:22,200 --> 00:30:24,440
Here you go. You want to study pharmacy, right?

511
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:26,288
First, read through this book. 
    

512
00:30:26,288 --> 00:30:27,845
